# GitHub Copilot Open Hack

Welcome to the GitHub Copilot Open Hack project! This repository is designed to help you learn and explore the capabilities of GitHub Copilot through various exercises and demos.

## Overview

This project contains:

1. A program for an open hack to learn GitHub Copilot.
2. Solutions to Copilot Adventures in Java.
3. Instructions for the GitHub Copilot Album Demo in Java Spring Boot.

## Open Hack Program

The open hack program is designed to provide hands-on experience with GitHub Copilot. You will work through a series of exercises and challenges to understand how Copilot can assist you in writing code more efficiently.

You can find the open hack program here: [Open Hack Program](Programme.md)

## Copilot Adventures in Java

In this section, you will find solutions to various Copilot Adventures in Java. These adventures are designed to showcase the capabilities of GitHub Copilot in solving common programming tasks and challenges in Java.

## GitHub Copilot Album Demo in Java Spring Boot

In this section, you will find instructions for the GitHub Copilot Album Demo in Java Spring Boot. This demo will guide you through creating a simple RESTful API for managing albums using GitHub Copilot.

### Instructions

For detailed instructions, please refer to the following documents:

1. [COPILOT_DEMOS.md](Challenges\gh-copilot-demo\1-COPILOT_DEMOS.md)
2. [COPILOT_CHAT_DEMOS.md](Challenges\gh-copilot-demo\2-COPILOT_CHAT_DEMOS.md)

